Need panel beating work done? Call Fleetcare Panel&Paint on 03 323 6345 . Located at 190E Maces Road, Bromley they are recognised specialists at repairing all types of vehicles by insurance companies, private motorists, and others in the trade&corporate sector. They can handle all types of repairs and vehicles, including trucks, boats, and caravans.
First impressions count in business so when you call Fleetcare Panel&Paint , you get the feeling that here is a company that is very professional in its approach and can be trusted to do a good job. It is particularly unwelcomed when you have just been involved in a road accident and take one look at the damaged vehicle and experience that sickening feeling in the stomach. You are not feeling great but decisions have to be made. The car has to be fixed. Private motorists might do well to get in touch with them knowing that Fleetcare Panel&Paint will do the job professionally. Fleetcare Panel&Paint have been busy repairing vehicles for all the leading insurers for years, and are also favoured by many firms with fleets in the corporate sector. Fleetcare Panel&Paint have a good reputation built on courtesy, sound practice, and a quick turnaround. They also specialise in custom air brush work which doesn’t just include cars, motorcycles, and trucks–they can customise just about anything, from helmets through to metal filing cabinets. If it can be painted, they can customise it!
